{"title":"Diet Nutrition Products","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"\u003eTo add a delightful taste of nutrition to your daily life snacking munching, Neuherbs diet nutrition range consists of a wide variety of tasty yet \u003cspan style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.neuherbs.com\/\" style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003enutritious foods\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e. These foods include seeds, seeds mixes with nuts some berries, along with peanut butter oats. These seeds mix can be utilized for maintaining good health with some crunch nutty taste. \u003cspan style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.neuherbs.com\/collections\/peanut-butter\" style=\"color: #167a62;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePeanut butter\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e could be a healthy substitute of protein for vegans of lactose intolerance that can help fulfil protein needs and can be used as an evening snack. Whereas, oats could be a highly nutritious, appetizing breakfast to kick-start your day to keep you active throughout the day. The good thing is you can have these in your diet in your own way in different recipes.\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"organic-pumpkin-seeds-heart-health","title":"Organic Pumpkin Seeds: Raw, Unroasted for Energy Boost","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eIndian pumpkin seeds are highly nutritious and are associated with multiple health benefits, including heart and brain health. Pumpkin seeds can also promote restful sleep. neuherbs unroasted, raw pumpkin seeds are sourced ethically from the best organic farms in India.\u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e  \u003c\/span\u003eThe pumpkin seeds contain potassium, magnesium, fiber, zinc, iron, healthy fats, and protein. They are rich in flavonoids and phenolic acid, which are essential antioxidants. The seeds also contain a very essential amount of Vitamin E.\u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e  \u003c\/span\u003ePumpkin seeds can be easily added to your daily diet. They can be eaten as evening snacks, either raw or roasted with spices or just salt. Taking pumpkin seeds regularly may help you manage many dietary problems. It may protect you from various health problems, including lowering cholesterol levels, improving energy, optimizing immune function, controlling blood sugar, improving digestive health, and regulating mood. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (1KG)","offer_id":40970885234858,"sku":"NPS1000","price":949.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Organic_pumpkin_seeds_1.png?v=1742561026"},{"product_id":"sunflower-seeds","title":"Organic Sunflower Seeds are rich in Vitamin E, unsaturated fatty acids, potassium \u0026 naturally sodium-free helps in heart \u0026 skin health","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: JA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\" lang=\"EN-US\"\u003eneuherbs Sunflower Seeds are a rich source of Vitamin E, unsaturated fatty acids, potassium, and anti-inflammatory properties that play a significant role in helping you manage common health problems, including body inflammation, skin issues, \u0026amp; heart health. Magnesium and unsaturated fatty acids like PUFA \u0026amp; MUFA present in sunflower seeds are known to maintain healthy blood pressure levels, and lower bad cholesterol levels when consumed regularly. The sunflower seeds also contain Vitamin B6, B5, Zinc, Protein, Manganese, and Selenium in small amounts. neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003esunflower seeds, organically cultivated in the best Indian farms, are rich in Vitamin E that functions as an essential antioxidant that protects your body from oxidative stress caused by free radical damage. These antioxidants also help reduce inflammation. neuherbs sunflower seeds are deshelled so that you can have them without effort. Sunflower seeds make a perfect, guilt-free snack. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (1KG)=Recommended","offer_id":40971419189418,"sku":"NSS1000","price":599.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/sunflower_seeds_1.png?v=1747304381"},{"product_id":"flax-seeds","title":"Raw Unroasted Flax Seeds naturally rich in Omega-3 fatty acids Helps in cholesterol levels, weight loss or management and strong Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eIf a healthy snack option is what you seek, which can not only reduce your hunger but also provide essential nutrients, neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eflax seeds are your answer. \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eneuherbs ’ organic, raw, and unroasted flax seeds provide Omega-3 fatty acids, like ALA, protein, calcium, and fiber. This makes it a fantastic meal maker for weight loss management and optimal heart health. It can help reduce inflammation, manage cholesterol levels, and regulate BP. The soluble fiber in neuherbs flaxseeds helps slow down digestion, regulate blood sugar levels, and reduce hunger, while the insoluble fiber promotes better bowel movements. You can add neuherbs Organic Flaxseeds to your smoothies, overnight oats, burger dough, bread dough, pancake batter, and nutrition bars or you can have them raw as your go-to snack, to avail maximum benefits for your health. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (1 KG)=Recommended","offer_id":40971567726762,"sku":"NFS1000","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/1kgflax_5.jpg?v=1731058797"},{"product_id":"organic-chia-seeds-health-boost-weight-loss-1","title":"Organic Chia Seeds for Weight Loss \u0026 Boost Health","description":"\u003cp style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eChia Seeds are a powerhouse of nutrients, primarily dietary fiber, omega –3 fatty acids, protein, magnesium, calcium, and antioxidants. These essential nutrients help manage weight, strengthen bones, regulate blood sugar levels, and improve skin health. Rich in both fiber and protein, including chia seeds in your daily diet can effectively curb hunger pangs, potentially reducing chances of overeating and late-night cravings. Rich in Omega 3 fatty acids and high in antioxidants, neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003enatural, raw \u0026amp; unroasted chia seeds offer a powerful punch of nutritional wellness. Our chia seeds for weight loss are premium grade and sourced organically from the best farms in India. Chia seeds have a mild nutty flavour and can be used in smoothies, oatmeal toppings, salads, or porridges, or can be added in water as well. You can also add neuherbs Chia Seeds to baked goods for tasty yet healthy nutritional punch.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (500GM)","offer_id":44202808737962,"sku":"NCS500","price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - (1KG)","offer_id":44266511925418,"sku":"NCS1000","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/chia_500g_front.jpg?v=1728478343"},{"product_id":"quinoa-seeds","title":"Raw Unroasted White Quinoa Seeds Rich in Protein, Iron, Fiber and Gluten Free Helps in cholesterol levels, weight loss and strong Bones","description":"\u003cp style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\" lang=\"EN-US\"\u003eQuinoa seeds are high in quality protein containing all essential amino acids, gluten-free, and loaded with vitamins \u0026amp; minerals. This means that people with wheat allergies can consume it without worry. They are also rich in magnesium, dietary fiber, vitamin B complex, vitamin E, calcium, and phosphorous, making them a wholesome, filling, and nutrient-dense superfood. In addition, they contain a large number of antioxidants, including flavonoids and phenolic acids. Quinoa seeds organic can help neutralize free radicals that cause oxidative stress in your body, protecting your body’s immune system. Include neuherbs unroasted, raw, organic white quinoa seeds to your diet and experience enhanced benefits – from managing weight to building muscles. It is an exceptional plant-based complete protein source for vegans and vegetarians. This is one of its unique qualities, as the majority of plant proteins are not complete proteins except quinoa.\u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e  \u003c\/span\u003eIn fact, it contains more protein, fat, and fiber than other grains. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (1KG)=Recommended","offer_id":40972565872810,"sku":"NQS1000-1","price":319.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard25_1.jpg?v=1726730281"},{"product_id":"super-seeds-mix-pumpkin-sunflower-flax","title":"Super Seeds Mix: Pumpkin, Sunflower \u0026 Flax for Heart, Brain \u0026 Joints","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Super Seeds Mix is a combination of raw, pure, unroasted and natural Pumpkin, Sunflower and Flax Seeds.These seeds help you fill the gap in your nutritional profile by addressing the effects of modern lifestyle on health. neuherbs seeds are sourced ethically from the best organic farms in India.  The pumpkin seeds contain potassium, magnesium, fibre, zinc, iron, healthy fats, and protein. They are rich in flavonoids and phenolic acid, which are essential antioxidants. On the other hand,  neuherbs organically sourced raw, and unroasted flax seeds provide Omega-3 fatty acids, like ALA, protein, calcium, and fiber. This makes it a fantastic meal maker for weight loss management and optimal heart health. And lastly, neuherbs sunflower seeds are a rich source of Vitamin E, unsaturated fatty acids, potassium, and anti-inflammatory properties that play a significant role in helping you manage daily wellness concerns including healthy skin \u0026amp; heart— making it just the right choice for our heart health friendly Super seeds mix. This super seeds mix can be easily added to your daily diet. They can also be eaten as evening snacks, either raw or roasted with spices or just salt. You can add them to your diets in a plethora of ways, and manage your heart health with the goodness of our Super Seeds Mix.\u003cbr\u003e\"\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (200 Gm + 400 Gm + 200 Gm)","offer_id":43368336621738,"sku":"NFSPSSSC3","price":513.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard2_4_6fa2baf0-300e-41ec-bc33-a1fc5b323d68.jpg?v=1731312795"},{"product_id":"sunflower-pumpkin-seeds-combo","title":"Sunflower \u0026 Pumpkin Seeds Combo - Heart \u0026 Skin Health","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 12.0pt 0cm 12.0pt 0cm;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eneuherbs Sunflower \u0026amp; Pumpkin Seeds Combo offers a nutritious and delicious snack that is packed with essential nutrients. These seeds are a rich source of healthy fats, protein, fiber, vitamins and minerals. Sunflowers seeds are known for their high content of vitamin E, which helps protect cells from damage. Pumpkin seeds are a great source of zinc, magnesium, and iron, which are essential for various bodily functions, help boost energy \u0026amp; maintain healthy heart. Enjoy this wholesome snack as a convenient and tasty way to boost your overall health and well-being.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (200 GM + 200GM)","offer_id":43368341078186,"sku":"NPSSSC2","price":364.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard2_5.jpg?v=1731054654"},{"product_id":"healthy-seeds-mix","title":"Healthy Seeds Mix rich in Vitamin E, healthy fats \u0026 Omega-3 for Heart \u0026 Brain, Immunity \u0026 Bones and Hair \u0026 Skin","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: JA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"\u003eMade with seeds that carry their own unique benefits, neuherbs Healthy Seeds Mix brings the comprehensive benefits of Pumpkin, Sunflower, Watermelon, Flax and Chia seeds, all packaged in one mix to help you achieve your overall health goals. Being rich in protein, healthy fat, essential vitamins \u0026amp; minerals, neuherbs Healthy Seeds Mix makes a great \u0026amp; healthy option for your untimely hunger cravings. This 5-in-One mix can be enjoyed anytime of the day whether for breakfast with oatmeal \u0026amp; juices or as a late-night munching snack. neuherbs Healthy Seeds Mix can be your wellness companion. Keep it while travelling, going to the office or hiking, it gives you a boost of energy, supports a healthy gut, immunity, heart, brain \u0026amp; bones. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (200 GM)","offer_id":42510508687530,"sku":"NHSM200","price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard10_40377185-7ff9-4ce0-b8a1-988ba2a92bd9.jpg?v=1718158877"},{"product_id":"flax-chia-seeds-combo-heart-health-weight-loss","title":"Flax \u0026 Chia Seeds Combo - Heart Health, Weight Loss, \u0026 Nutrition","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Flaxseed \u0026amp; Chia Seed Combo offers a nutritious and versatile blend of two superfoods. Organic flaxseeds are packed with fiber, omega-3 fatty acids, and lignans, promoting heart, bone health, and gut balance. Organic chia seeds are a rich source of fiber, protein, omega-3 fatty acids, and antioxidants, supporting healthy weight, skin and overall well-being. This powerful combination provides a convenient way to incorporate essential nutrients into your daily diet.  \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (400 GM + 200 GM)","offer_id":43368355922090,"sku":"NFSCSC2","price":318.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard1_3_68ba8403-347b-4054-955a-cb8ffc5bd193.jpg?v=1731310829"},{"product_id":"flax-chia-pumpkin-sunflower-seeds-combo","title":"Nutrient-Rich Combo: Flax, Chia, Pumpkin \u0026 Sunflower Seeds","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Pumpkin, Sunflower, Chia \u0026amp; Flax Seeds Combo offers a nutritious and versatile blend of superfoods. Pumpkin seeds are packed with protein, zinc, and magnesium, while sunflower seeds provide essential fatty acids and vitamin E. Chia and flax seeds are rich in fiber, omega-3 fatty acids, and antioxidants. This combination is a convenient way to add a boost of nutrients to your diet, supporting heart health, digestion, and overall well-being. \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (400g + 200g + 200g + 200g)","offer_id":43368366309546,"sku":"NFSCSPSSSC4","price":682.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard1_2_2_9682c0be-ac7a-412a-aa4c-6612e052db7f.jpg?v=1731311731"},{"product_id":"organic-flax-chia-pumpkin-seeds-combo","title":"Organic Flax, Chia \u0026 Pumpkin Seeds Combo for Heart \u0026 Bone Health","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003eneuherbs Flax Chia Pumpkin Seed Combo offers a powerful blend of nutrient-rich seeds. Flaxseeds provide essential omega-3 fatty acids, fiber, and lignans, supporting heart health and hormone balance. Chia seeds are packed with fiber, protein, and antioxidants, promoting digestive health and energy levels. Pumpkin seeds are a rich source of zinc, magnesium, and healthy fats, supporting immunity and brain function. This synergistic combination provides a daily dose of essential nutrients to nourish your body and promote overall well-being.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (200 GM + 400 GM + 200 GM)","offer_id":43368358412458,"sku":"NFSCSPSC3","price":533.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard1_3_618f2977-08ef-4cab-82bb-96dff4df7986.jpg?v=1731312570"},{"product_id":"protein-seeds-mix-sunflower-pumpkin-seeds-protein","title":"Protein Seeds Mix - Rich in Protein, Dietary Fiber, Magnesium","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: JA; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"\u003eGet your daily protein intake with Protein Seed Mix by neuherbs- a nutritious and delicious high-protein superfood that supports your fitness goals naturally. Protein seeds mix contain a good amount of pumpkin seeds, watermelon seeds, and sunflower seeds. These organically grown seeds are a great plant-based source of protein and dietary fibers. They are also packed with essential vitamins and minerals that our mind \u0026amp; body needs on a daily basis. neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eall-natural protein mix not only provides your body with all the nutrients but also serves as a low-calorie snack that satisfies your food cravings, keeping you satiated for longer. You can use neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eprotein seeds mix in a variety of dishes, such as kheer, laddoo, shakes, smoothies, oatmeal, and panjiri. neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eProtein Seeds Mix may not burn fat or build muscles, however, this plant-based protein mix, contains ingredients that possess nutrients and dietary fiber that can support your fitness goals when you do the right exercises and eat a balanced diet.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (200 GM)","offer_id":43374043857066,"sku":"NPSM200","price":199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/protein_seeds_mix_1.jpg?v=1748865202"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/diet-nutrition-products.oembed","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}